FAtravels wrote a review Jan 2024
England, United Kingdom23 contributions23 helpful votes
Minh House is the best in Da Nang!
Stopped in Da Nang at Minh House for one night - what a wonderful experience! Minh House staff (Vi and the rest of the team) were SO welcoming, attentive and go above and beyond for you. The room and hotel itself is stunning - modern, clean, beautiful. We both had a great, restful night sleep as the bed was huge and super comfortable. The breakfast was delicious and as soon as we entered the breakfast room, we were greeted with coffees, fruit and pastries and then a little later, our ordered breakfast. Minh House made our short stay in Da Nang perfect and we would recommend to all!
Read more
Date of stay: January 2024
