Vic wrote a review Nov 2023
Torrejon De Ardoz, Spain10 contributions
Warm hotel with kind staff, comfy rooms and close to the beach
The people working at the hotel couldn't be nicer, always friendly and attentive. The rooms were decorated with a modern touch, comfy beds, and with everything you need at a hotel. The pool was nice, and the breakfast was very good. Location was superb, close to the beach. Totally recommendable if you're spending a few days in Da Nang. ;)
Date of stay: November 2023
