Lovely stay at. Minh house
Relaxing and cozy stay. Nice location, 10 min to the beach and 20 min walking to the expat district, where you can find nice reactants and cafes. You can also take a grap car for $ 2 Also lots of local food, that you can try on the surroundings. Also really quite with a beautiful pool
