Nha Vo Thanh wrote a review Jan 2020
1 contribution
Review on my stay from 18 Jan - 19 Jan 2020
My stay was pleasant. The staff in the hotel are very kind. The hotel is within walking distance to the beach. For breakfast, they offer local foods and western foods. Personally, I did like the local food "beef stew", which is translated as "bo kho" in Vietnamese, which I tried during my stay. For facilities, since the hotel doesn't have a lift, that might be problematic if you carry a large suitcase. So, this might be the thing that the hotel could improve. In short, I would recommend this hotel. Definitely, I would stay there if I visit Da Nang again.
Date of stay: January 2020
