Addis Ababa, Ethiopia49 contributions3 helpful votes
+1
Feels like meeting long time friends
Very welcoming staff at our first entry and during the whole stay. Felt like we were long time friends. Very nice and calm hotel, nice design of rooms. Bed very comfortable. In rooms during whole days relaxing music ( can be put off). Very near the DaNang beach. If you turn to left from hotel you will enter in a nice part of town, full of hotels, restos, coffeeshops and massage opportunities. But a 20 minutes walk away from the Dragon vridge and coty center. Breakfast very good and prepared by charming Ema who presented a daily varied breakfast. Reception staff very professional, interested and always ready to assist you. Special thanks to Mya, Nhi and Tina. Mya came back special from Minh boutique to say us goodbye. Hotel to be recommended to all ! Staff organised trip for usâ€¦
